gml:Definition.gml:description: Roads used exclusively for motor vehicle traffic, and are used to handle large volumes of wide-area traffic at high speeds. National freeways, urban expressways, general motorways.
Urban road that forms the backbone of the city as well as handle the mass traffic within the city.
Road closely related to daily life that form the outer boundaries of city blocks and residential areas.
Roads used for special traffic other than automobile traffic.
